author: uing
title: BIGSTAR’s Baram To Enlist In Mandatory Military Service Soon
text:
Display.Sharethrough.Soompi.1x1 
BIGSTAR’s Baram is enlisting in the mandatory military service soon. 
His agency Brave Entertainment announced on February 24, “Baram will enlist on February 27 to receive his basic military training for four weeks and serve as a public service worker for 23 months. Please continue to support him.” 
Baram expressed, “I figured I should complete my service before it gets too late. I will return to my fans in two years as an improved person.” 
Good luck to Baram!
